<div>
<p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface font-bold">Severe Wind Gusts</p>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Expected in 45 mins. Secure sheds.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Medium Alert -->
