<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-container">storm</span>
<div>
<p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface font-bold">Heavy Rain (80%)</p>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Evening forecast. Check drainage.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Advisory -->
